beer.beer_description: Using ginger 100% sourced from Queensland, this thirst-quenching sessionable ginger beer is the perfect foil for hot summer days. Hurricane Head was born in the sub-tropics with their thirst-breaking lager, now their entry into ginger beer is the perfect storm. Refreshing and delicious, think aromas and flavours of sweet spicy ginger with a hint of vanilla.
